DataElement.preferredDefinition: Widespread, broadly dispersed, common._Any procedure that involves testing or manipulating a sample of blood, urine, or other body substance in a laboratory setting.:A string unique to a time duration of 24 hours between 2 successive midnights defined by the local time zone. The specific representation of a date will depend on which calendar convention is in force as well as local ordering conventions._The sweet edible fruit of the date palm with a single long woody seed._A laboratory test designed for the quantification of an organic or inorganic chemical within a biological specimen._The particular day, month and year an event has happened or will happen._Generic value domain for a java datatype that represents a specific instant in time, with millisecond precision.
